# cash flow 
	- expenses	支出
	- income	收入

# assets
	- deposit	存款
		- Time Deposits		定期存款
		- Demand Deposits	活期存款

	- exchange 	外匯
		- cash	現鈔
		- Spot Time Deposits 	即期-定期存款
		- Spot Demand Deposits	即期-活期存款
		- buying rate 	買入匯率
		- selling rate	賣出匯率	

	- stock		股票
		- Margin Trading 融資
		- Short Selling 融卷		

	- fund		基金
	- bond		債券
	- account receivable	應收帳款
	- account payable		應負帳款